---
import ThankYouLayout from '../../layouts/ThankYouLayout.astro';
---

<ThankYouLayout
  productSlug="trust-architecture-blueprint"
  description="Your Trust Architecture Blueprint is ready to download."
  readyLine="Your Trust Architecture Blueprint is ready."
  downloadHeading="Download your blueprint"
  downloadHref="/downloads/Trust-Architecture-Blueprint-v1.0.pdf"
>
  <Fragment slot="download-description">
    <p>The Trust Architecture Blueprint is a four-pillar framework for building trust into autonomous systems - identity, memory, governance, and refusal rights. Includes templates for persona files, session protocols, graduated trust stages, and quarterly reviews.</p>
    <p>Start with Part 1: Identity Architecture. Everything else builds on it.</p>
  </Fragment>

  <Fragment slot="next-steps">
    <a href="/products/trust-architecture-blueprint" class="pd-upsell-card">
      <h3>Build your first persona file</h3>
      <p>Use the template in Part 1 to define your first agent's identity, boundaries, and voice.</p>
      <span class="pd-upsell-link">Open the blueprint page &rarr;</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/products/agent-governance-starter-kit" class="pd-upsell-card">
      <h3>Go deeper</h3>
      <p>Pair this with the Agent Governance Starter Kit for charter and accountability templates, or the Agent Voice Architecture Guide for voice design.</p>
      <span class="pd-upsell-link">See the Starter Kit &rarr;</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/fit" class="pd-upsell-card">
      <h3>Check your fit</h3>
      <p>A 5-minute fit assessment to see which Evoke services align with where you are right now.</p>
      <span class="pd-upsell-link">Take the assessment &rarr;</span>
    </a>
    <a href="https://cal.com/cal.com-evoked/discovery-call" class="pd-upsell-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      <h3>Talk it through</h3>
      <p>Book a free 30-minute discovery call to discuss your trust architecture.</p>
      <span class="pd-upsell-link">Schedule &rarr;</span>
    </a>
  </Fragment>
</ThankYouLayout>
